logId.description: ID of the time log entry.

userId.description: ID of the user who logged the time.

date.description: The date of the time log.

userName.description: Name of the user who logged the time.

clientId.description: ID of the client associated with the time log.

clientName.description: Name of the client associated with the time log.

projectId.description: ID of the project associated with the time log.

projectName.description: Name of the project associated with the time log.

taskId.description: ID of the task associated with the time log.

taskName.description: Name of the task associated with the time log.

tags.description: Tags associated with the time log.

rate.description: Rate applicable for the time log.

billable.description: Boolean indicating if the time is billable.

inLockedPeriod.description: Indicates if the time log is in a locked period.

billableAmount.description: The amount billable for the logged time.

amount.description: The total amount of time logged.

laborCost.description: The labor cost for the time logged.

laborRate.description: Rate of labor for the time log.

expense.description: Expenses associated with the time log.

cost.description: The cost incurred for the time logged.

note.description: Additional notes related to the time log.

invoiceId.description: The ID of the invoice associated with the time log.

invoiced.description: Indicates if the time log has been invoiced.

billableHours.description: The number of billable hours logged.

monthOfYear.description: Month of the year for the time log.

weekOfYear.description: Week of the year for the time log.

times.description: Time entries within the time log.

startTime.description: Start time of the time entry.

endTime.description: End time of the time entry.

running.description: Indicates if the time entry is running.

deleted.description: Indicates if the time entry is deleted.

attachments.description: Attachments associated with the time log.

balance.description: The remaining balance after time logging.

billableExpense.description: Indicates if expenses are billable for the time logged.

billableHoursLogBillable.description: The billable hours for log billing.

clientCustomId.description: Custom ID of the client associated with the time log.

endTime.description: The end time of the logged time.

invoicedAmount.description: The amount already invoiced for the time log.

logDurationBillable.description: Billable duration of the time log.

startTime.description: The start time of the logged time.

teams.description: Teams associated with the time log.

teamsNames.description: Names of teams associated with the time log.

taskDueDate.description: Due date for the associated task.

taskStartDate.description: Start date for the associated task.

uninvoicedAmount.description: Amount yet to be invoiced for the time-log.
